<center><table BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=20 COLS=1 WIDTH="100%" BGCOLOR="#BAFFFF" >
<tr>
<td><font size=-1>In Scotland, the fyrst Pestilens</font>
<br><font size=-1>Begouth, off sa gret wyolens,</font>
<br><font size=-1>That, it wes sayd, off lywand men</font>
<br><font size=-1>The thryd part it dystroyid then,</font>
<br><font size=-1>Efftyr that in till Scotland</font>
<br><font size=-1>A yhere, or mare, it was wedand</font>
<br><font size=-1>Before that tyme wes nevyr sene</font>
<br><font size=-1>A pestilens in oure land sa kene:</font>
<br><font size=-1>Bathe men, and barnys, and women,</font>
<br><font size=-1>It sparyd noucht for to kille them.</font>
<blockquote>
 <font size=-1>--Andrew of Wyntoun</font>
            <br>
            <font size=-1>&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>Orygynale Cronykil</i> (1420)</font></blockquote>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</center></td>
